<p>周二（8月4日）：加拿大八月以假期重启（Canada reopens from August holiday）</p>
<p>专业交易员提示：警惕羊群效应，注意主要支撑位及阻力位。（If you run with the herd, you may get trampled. Be aware of major support and resistance levels.）</p>
